  "texts": [
    "Eluted nanobodies were further purified by size exclusion chromatography using a Superdex 75 10/300 column equilibrated in PBS on an Akta Pure System (Cytiva) to remove the imidazole, further increase the purity and isolate monomeric nanobodies.",
    "Purified nanobodies were aliquoted, flash-frozen in liquid nitrogen and stored at -80 °C.",
    "Each aliquot was used only once and, following thawing, was centrifuged at 21,000g at 4 °C for 10 min to pellet down any precipitate that may have formed during freeze-thawing.",
    "Recombinant β 2 -microglobulin was expressed and purified to homogeneity as previously reported in ref. 83.",
    "Briefly, E. coli BL21(DE3) cells were transformed with pET29b carrying the coding sequence of β 2 -microglobulin."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}